highlights.text: “PLAY OUT LOUD” by TENBLANK is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Hong Kong, up 37 spots at #31.
“零距离的思念” by TINY 7 has been on Viral Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 135 days straight.
G.E.M. has the most spots on Viral Songs Hong Kong. “天空没有極限 (粤)” is the highest at #26.
“Where Did U Go (G.E.M.重生版)” by G.E.M. is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Hong Kong at #92.
